# 10-Second Interview Cheat Sheet

| Problem Signal | Pattern |
|---------------|----------|
| Range Query | Prefix Sum |
| Count Subarray Sum | Prefix + HashMap |
| For Every Index | Auxiliary Arrays |
| Sorted + Pair | Two Pointers |
| Palindrome | Two Pointers |
| Contiguous + Longest | Sliding Window |
| Contiguous + Shortest | Sliding Window |
| Window Size K | Fixed Sliding Window |
| Maximum Subarray Sum | Kadane |
| Top K | Heap |
| Next Greater Element | Stack |
| Minimum Possible X | Binary Search |

---

# Master Recognition Formula

1. Range Query → Prefix Sum
2. Sorted + Pair → Two Pointers
3. Contiguous + Longest/Shortest → Sliding Window
4. Contiguous + Maximum Sum → Kadane
5. Need Left/Right Information → Auxiliary Arrays
